{
  "stem": "4764.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe it's more traumatic than I imagine, or maybe it has it had an influence on my performance or thinking, et cetera, that, that, I've suppressed it to such an extent that I can't-- I can't bring it out of the, the deep recesses of my mind.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe under hypnotherapy I could.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But maybe I don't want to do that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe it's not necessary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think it's been traumatic enough.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I didn't realize that just retelling the story that I would be so emotional [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to me, now it's been such a long time.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I'm glad I'm Jewish, in spite of everything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think-- and I've tried to instill this in my children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I put them through a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I think that there are now such forces outside, in which-- which influence us to such an extent that there is enough out there-- how shall I put it-- that will take away from our Jewishness, you see?",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if you don't give them this sort of background to start off with, there's no point blaming them, if things go against what you think is right.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because you haven't instilled them into it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If they do things which you don't think is right, at least you've given that start in life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they can make up their own mind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The most important thing is, is happiness, of course.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I think it's good to have a Jewish upbringing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My first wife was against-- she's more, I'll say, liberal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She wanted them to have a more rounded education and meet people of, of other races and other religions.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because it tends to be a little bit homophobic being in a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I don't think that this has happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
